channel.title: Importing 614 into a 562
channel.description:
Hello
I've been getting a lot of requests to add 614 items into my base, which is a 562. Is it possible to add 614 items into a 562 base or has this even been attempted or am I simply rambling?
I jar my own client and control my cache, so if anyone can point me to some information on this, I would be grateful!
-Chris/Kizz
